Author: ap0cryphal
Text: I feel you. Protein bars are my top safe food took, but the high cost means that I don’t have many of them, so whenever I have free food in front of me, I overeat to compensate. rip  I’m sorry for your loss and I hope you are able to enjoy the weekend. 💝

Author: tulipsandmothballs
Text: Happy birthday! I hope you can find just a minute of peace and enjoy your bday, even just for a moment.
